'''Tolkien Calendar 1995''' was published by Seckji Tolkienowskiej Slaskiego Kluba Fantastyki, Poland ([[Polish Tolkien Society]]). The calendar features pen and ink illustrations by [[Maciej Wygnanski]], [[Aleksandra Jagielowica]], [[Małgorzata Pudlik]], Marek Dabrowski, and [[Karolina Stopa]].

* Dimensions: 11 5/8 x 8 1/4 inches
* Heavy, clear plastic cover sheet
* Blue plastic comb-bound
